    {
      "chinese": "如果部落有人去世，一定要遵守治喪忌諱。如果不遵守，將導致住家倒塌，被雷劈打，田地也將流失。治喪時間家屬及親屬為七天，同部落則為三天。",
      "ab": "Maca maiza ca bunun mataz, asat masimaupas kaisamuas iniqumicas Bunun qabas, tis’unis minataz a bunun dii huzanghuzang saukanaqtung. Uuca nii’ a, na mintunuq dau ca lumaq, lanada’as bicvaq, munqanu’ ca quma. Uuca kinuzan is malkaciat minataz a bununi’ huzanghuzang, na pitu’ ta’ diqanin ca kinuzas tatlumaq ciin tastusiduq a bunun, na taau diqanin ca pandu’as tastu’acang bunun mintudaidaz piscacalpu.",
